Frank Elliott (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Elliott_(actor) 0 Frank Elliott (11 February 1880 – July 1970) was an English film actor. He appeared in 77 films between 1915 and 1966. He was born in Cheshire, England. Frank_Elliott ( 11_February_1880 – July 1970 ) was an_English_film_actor . He appeared in 77_films between 1915_and_1966 . He was_born in Cheshire , England .
